<!-- Tabaxi Xenotype -->
	<XenotypeDef>
		<defName>Joe_Tabaxi_Xeno</defName>
		<label>tabaxi</label>
		<description>Hailing from the strange and distant land of the Feywild, wandering tabaxi are catlike humanoids whose hearts beat with restless curiosity and wonder. Born amidst shimmering groves, moonlit glades, and time-twisted paths, these feline folk carry the enchantment of their homeland in every graceful step. The Feywild’s magic infuses them with an irrepressible urge to explore, to collect curious artifacts, to gather tales and stories, and to lay eyes on all the world's wonders. Ultimate travelers, the inquisitive tabaxi rarely stay in one place for long. Their innate nature pushes them to leave no secret uncovered, no treasure or legend forgotten. To a tabaxi, the world is a tapestry of mysteries waiting to be unraveled—and they are the nimble threads that dance across it.</description>
		<descriptionShort>Tabaxi are inquisitive, catlike humanoids known for their curiosity and their restless nature.</descriptionShort>
